.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/019-skill-doc-alignment-and-changelog-consolidation/spec.md:60:This is the closeout phase for packet 121. The two-arc program (phases 001-018) reshaped the `deep-agent-improvement` skill — a new model-benchmark mode and a two-lane (Lane A / Lane B) architecture — but two doc surfaces lagged: the skill `README.md` still described the pre-121 flat single-lane layout, and the skill's changelog captured only the two-lane arc (008-013) as `v1.9.0.0.md`, leaving the build arc (001-007) and the review/remediation phases (014-018) un-summarized.
