.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/011-agent-lane-note/spec.md:61:This is **Phase 11** of the deep-agent-improvement benchmark-mode parent packet. Phase 009 restructured SKILL.md so model-benchmark became co-equal Lane B. This phase carries that two-lane framing into the @deep-agent-improvement agent file and its 3 runtime mirrors.
