.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/016-script-subfolder-readmes/spec.md:59:This is **Phase 16** of the two-lane deep-agent-improvement program. The two-lane reorg (phases 008-015) moved scripts into `agent-improvement/`, `model-benchmark/`, and `shared/` lane subtrees, plus a nested `model-benchmark/scorer/` tree. The on-disk lane layout is now stable, but most lane folders have no local README.
