.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/015-fix-deep-review-findings-for-two-lane-code/decision-record.md:536:| F-P1-8 | P1 | Explicit Lane B shadowed by agent-path check order | FIXED | Resolve explicit lane before agent-path inference; fail fast on conflict |
