.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/015-fix-deep-review-findings-for-two-lane-code/plan.md:48:Remediate the 014 deep-review findings against the two-lane program. The single P0 is a parser mismatch: the Lane B command surfaces pass SPACE-form flags that `loop-host.cjs` `parseArgs` cannot read. Fix the parser to accept both `--key=value` and `--key value` while keeping the `=`-form path byte-identical (TST-1 safe), then harden the P1 security cluster (read-only grader dispatch, quoted YAML interpolation, fixture-id traversal guard, fail-closed criteria-exec, packet-local owner-checked cache) and the P1 traceability cluster (valid outcomes, threaded executor fields, plateau stop, consolidated config, provenance, lane ordering, candidate-keyed cache, immutable reports, packet-local pause, corrected promotion gate, repointed agent notes). Every P2 gets a FIXED or DOCUMENT-ACCEPT disposition.
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/015-fix-deep-review-findings-for-two-lane-code/plan.md:73:Lane-separated CommonJS scripts under `scripts/{shared,agent-improvement,model-benchmark}/` plus `scripts/lib/`, driven by `loop-host.cjs` which plans an invocation per mode and spawns step scripts. Lane B planning forwards parsed flags into `materialize-benchmark-fixtures.cjs` then `run-benchmark.cjs`; `dispatch-model.cjs` loads only on `--grader llm`.
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/015-fix-deep-review-findings-for-two-lane-code/plan.md:76:- **`loop-host.cjs` (shared)**: `parseArgs`, `resolveMode`, `planInvocation`, `resolveScriptPath`. Owns the P0 parser fix and executor-field threading.
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/015-fix-deep-review-findings-for-two-lane-code/plan.md:77:- **`run-benchmark.cjs` (model-benchmark)**: scores fixture outputs, writes `report.json`, appends ledger rows. Owns fixture-id sanitization, scorer provenance on failure, per-iteration reports, profile provenance.
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/015-fix-deep-review-findings-for-two-lane-code/plan.md:78:- **`dispatch-model.cjs` (model-benchmark)**: spawns external executors on `--grader llm`. Owns read-only sandbox default and packet-local pause state.
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/015-fix-deep-review-findings-for-two-lane-code/plan.md:79:- **`score-candidate.cjs` (agent-improvement)**: Lane A scorer with an on-disk score cache. Owns packet-local owner-checked cache and candidate-keyed cache key.
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/015-fix-deep-review-findings-for-two-lane-code/plan.md:80:- **`reduce-state.cjs` (shared)**: aggregates state; owns benchmark plateau stop and unknown-mode bucketing.
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/015-fix-deep-review-findings-for-two-lane-code/plan.md:81:- **Lane B YAMLs + command docs + agent mirrors + advisor scorer**: command-surface fixes.
