.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/002-implementation-deep-research/research/findings-registry.json:320:      "text": "Only when mode=`model-benchmark` should the ported 120/003 rubric path be activated",
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/002-implementation-deep-research/research/findings-registry.json:332:      "text": "The mode detection should be DONE in `loop.cjs` (or `reduce-state.cjs`), NOT inside the scorer itself — the scorer receives a pre-processed `scoringMode` argument",
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/002-implementation-deep-research/research/findings-registry.json:337:      "id": "finding-3-14-the-new-scorer-seam-must-default-to-the-existing-score-candidate-cjs-behavior-wh",
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/002-implementation-deep-research/research/findings-registry.json:338:      "text": "The new scorer seam MUST default to the existing `score-candidate.cjs` behavior when mode=`agent-improvement`",
