.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/002-implementation-deep-research/research/findings-registry.json:344:      "text": "The scorer NEVER reads a fixture JSON file directly — all fixture data is extracted and passed as primitives by the loop host",
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/002-implementation-deep-research/research/findings-registry.json:349:      "id": "finding-4-38-materialize-benchmark-fixtures-cjs-is-not-called-by-run-benchmark-cjs-they-are-s",
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/002-implementation-deep-research/research/findings-registry.json:350:      "text": "**materialize-benchmark-fixtures.cjs is not called by run-benchmark.cjs**: They are separate. The loop host must call materialize BEFORE run-benchmark. Omitting this step produces zero fixture outputs and all fixtures fail with `missing-output`.",
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/002-implementation-deep-research/research/findings-registry.json:361:      "id": "finding-4-37-no-loop-cjs-exists-yet-must-create-loop-host-cjs-as-the-new-orchestrating-entry-",
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/002-implementation-deep-research/research/findings-registry.json:362:      "text": "**No loop.cjs exists yet**: Must create loop-host.cjs as the new orchestrating entry point. Without this, there is no place to wire the mode switch.",
