.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/002-implementation-deep-research/research/findings-registry.json:368:      "text": "**Promote-candidate convergence for model-benchmark**: The convergence criteria (aggregate threshold, per-fixture minimum, pass rate) are per-profile from the benchmark profile JSON. These must be passed to promote-candidate.cjs or embedded in the benchmark_run record for it to read.",
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/002-implementation-deep-research/research/findings-registry.json:373:      "id": "finding-4-41-reduce-state-computes-per-profile-aggregates-if-model-benchmark-and-agent-improv",
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/002-implementation-deep-research/research/findings-registry.json:374:      "text": "**reduce-state computes per-profile aggregates**: If model-benchmark and agent-improvement records are mixed in the same state log, reduce-state correctly handles them via record.type routing. No special mixed-mode handling needed.",
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/002-implementation-deep-research/research/findings-registry.json:379:      "id": "finding-4-40-state-record-mode-field-must-be-consistent-if-score-candidate-emits-mode-agent-i",
