.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/context-index.md:76:1. **Renamed** the 4 phase folders above (`git mv` + self-reference path-fixes; 0 residual old-slug refs inside the renamed folders).
