.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/007-benchmark-mode-hardening-review/review/iterations/iteration-007.md:50:- Evidence: On a rate-limit response, the dispatcher selects waits from `BACKOFF_MS` and then spins in `while (Date.now() < sleepEnd) {}` (`dispatch-model.cjs:189-194`). With the configured defaults, that can block the Node process for minutes while consuming CPU, and there is no injectable sleep function or clock for a focused unit test.
