.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/017-two-lane-opus-deep-review/review/iterations/iteration-10.md:5:Second independent Opus 4.8 deep review of the deep-agent-improvement TWO-LANE program (phases 008-013), post-015-remediation. Iteration 10 of 10, dimension focus: **security**. Goal: (a) confirm 015 remediations hold without regression, (b) surface NEW security issues a different model finds, without re-reporting the 16 prior findings already in the feed-forward registry.
