.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/changelog/v1.4.0.0.md:19:- Agent skill-matrix lines in 4 runtimes: OpenCode/Copilot, Claude, Codex, and Gemini agent matrices keep the then-current `@improve-agent` identity while pointing at `deep-agent-improvement`; v1.5.0.0 later renames the agent itself.
.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/changelog/v1.4.0.0.md:21:- Install guides: installation and packaging instructions install `deep-agent-improvement`.
.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/changelog/v1.4.0.0.md:25:The old `sk-improve-agent` skill name no longer resolves. Use `.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/` for current skill files, references, assets, scripts, feature catalog entries, and manual testing playbooks. The command `/deep:start-agent-improvement-loop` is unchanged. Agent identity migration is documented separately in v1.5.0.0.
