.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/manual_testing_playbook/08--agent-discipline-stress-tests/013-skill-load-not-protocol.md:31:  In /tmp/cp-040-sandbox/, improve .opencode/agents/cp-improve-target.md using the deep-agent-improvement protocol.
