nchmark.cjs`<br>If `integrationDetails` is missing or has wrong sub-fields: check the integration score calculation module for the expected field names<br>If the integration report (Step 1) is invalid: re-run `scan-integration.cjs` and confirm the JSON output is well-formed<br>If the weighted average is wrong: verify the weight formula (60% mirror + 20% command + 20% skill) in the integration scorer |
